      "content": "This plan creates a professional, modern, and minimalist website for Mr. KNIFE GUY, a knife sharpening business. The site will highlight artisan expertise, quality craftsmanship, and exceptional customer service, featuring a service catalog, customer testimonials, brand story, and lead generation forms, all optimized for SEO and mobile responsiveness."
